894
01:14:01.229 --> 01:14:03.148
[Soldiers Cheer]

895
01:14:03.231 --> 01:14:05.191
[Applause]

896
01:14:07.819 --> 01:14:09.237
West: Hat.

897
01:14:10.447 --> 01:14:11.573
So...

898
01:14:11.656 --> 01:14:12.699
what have we here?

899
01:14:15.535 --> 01:14:16.953
Tinned ham. tinned peas...

900
01:14:17.037 --> 01:14:18.955
tinned beans. and—

901
01:14:23.710 --> 01:14:24.794
Soldier: Nice one. Doris.

902
01:14:24.878 --> 01:14:26.546
Omelet.

903
01:14:26.630 --> 01:14:27.756
You've prepared a feast. Jones.

904
01:14:27.839 --> 01:14:28.923
Honor of our guests. sir.

905
01:14:29.007 --> 01:14:30.050
Absolutely.

906
01:14:30.133 --> 01:14:32.302
I was going to propose a toast...

907
01:14:32.385 --> 01:14:34.721
but this omelet
will do just as well.

908
01:14:34.804 --> 01:14:36.389
[Plate Clanks]

909
01:14:38.183 --> 01:14:39.309
To new friends.

910
01:14:39.392 --> 01:14:40.769
Soldiers: New friends.

911
01:14:51.237 --> 01:14:52.822
Jones. did you notice
while cooking...

912
01:14:52.906 --> 01:14:53.907
that these eggs were off?

913
01:14:55.158 --> 01:14:57.577
I thought the salt
might cover the taste. sir.

914
01:14:58.745 --> 01:15:00.497
Get rid of it.

915
01:15:00.580 --> 01:15:02.874
[Forks Drop On Plates]

916
01:15:02.957 --> 01:15:04.000
Soldier: Doris. you twat.

917
01:15:04.084 --> 01:15:05.251
[Sighs]

918
01:15:05.335 --> 01:15:07.337
I don't suppose
you can cook. can you?

919
01:15:09.255 --> 01:15:10.840
I can't tell you
how badly we need...

920
01:15:10.924 --> 01:15:12.842
someone with a little
flair in the kitchen.

921
01:15:14.719 --> 01:15:16.805
What a fucking disappointment.

922
01:15:16.888 --> 01:15:17.889
When I saw those eggs...

923
01:15:17.972 --> 01:15:19.265
I thought it was Christmas.

924
01:15:19.349 --> 01:15:20.767
We'll all have eggs again...

925
01:15:20.850 --> 01:15:22.060
once everything's back to normal.

926
01:15:22.143 --> 01:15:23.520
Oh. you muppet.

927
01:15:23.603 --> 01:15:25.563
I mean. look at him. eh?

928
01:15:25.647 --> 01:15:26.564
Look. he's still waiting...

929
01:15:26.648 --> 01:15:28.024
for Marks and Spencer's to reopen.

930
01:15:28.108 --> 01:15:29.025
[Soldiers Laugh]

931
01:15:29.109 --> 01:15:30.610
Listen. mate.
you don't know nothing.

932
01:15:30.694 --> 01:15:32.487
Soldier: Well. I think
Bell's got a point.

933
01:15:34.114 --> 01:15:37.283
If you look at the whole
life of the planet...

934
01:15:37.367 --> 01:15:39.202
WE...

935
01:15:39.285 --> 01:15:40.537
you know. man...

936
01:15:40.620 --> 01:15:43.540
has only been around
for a few blinks of an eye.

937
01:15:43.623 --> 01:15:46.209
So if the infection
wipes us all out...

938
01:15:47.794 --> 01:15:50.046
that is a return to normality.

939
01:15:50.130 --> 01:15:51.047
[Chuckles]

940
01:15:54.217 --> 01:15:55.301
That what you meant. Bell?

941
01:15:55.385 --> 01:15:56.636
Yeah. yeah.

942
01:15:56.720 --> 01:15:57.637
West: Have you. uh...

943
01:15:57.721 --> 01:15:59.389
have you met our new-age sergeant?

944
01:15:59.472 --> 01:16:00.390
[Soldiers Laugh]

945
01:16:00.473 --> 01:16:02.642
Our spiritual guru.

946
01:16:02.726 --> 01:16:03.643
Tell me. Farrell...

947
01:16:03.727 --> 01:16:06.187
exactly why did you join the army...

948
01:16:06.271 --> 01:16:07.188
in the first place?

949
01:16:11.151 --> 01:16:12.068
This is what I've seen...

950
01:16:12.152 --> 01:16:15.280
in the 4 weeks
since infection—

951
01:16:15.363 --> 01:16:17.157
People killing people...

952
01:16:18.324 --> 01:16:19.409
which is much what I saw...

953
01:16:19.492 --> 01:16:20.910
in the 4 weeks before infection...

954
01:16:20.994 --> 01:16:22.120
and the 4 weeks before that...

955
01:16:22.203 --> 01:16:23.121
and before that.

956
01:16:23.204 --> 01:16:24.831
As far back as I care to remember...

957
01:16:24.914 --> 01:16:26.750
people killing people...

958
01:16:27.834 --> 01:16:28.793
which. to my mind...

959
01:16:28.877 --> 01:16:31.171
puts us in a state
of normality right now.

960
01:16:31.254 --> 01:16:33.423
- [Man Grunting]
- [Footsteps]

961
01:16:40.305 --> 01:16:41.931
You're not eating?

962
01:16:42.015 --> 01:16:43.266
I don't want to eat.

963
01:16:43.349 --> 01:16:45.101
You must eat. Hannah.

964
01:16:45.185 --> 01:16:47.562
I don't want to eat.

965
01:16:47.645 --> 01:16:50.398
I want to bury my dad.

966
01:16:50.482 --> 01:16:52.609
He's one of the people
you're talking about.

967
01:16:55.987 --> 01:16:57.197
[Explosion]

968
01:16:57.280 --> 01:16:58.740
Stand to! Stand to!

969
01:16:58.823 --> 01:17:00.033
Soldier: Go! Go! Go! Go!

970
01:17:00.116 --> 01:17:01.034
Farrell: Move it. men!

971
01:17:02.827 --> 01:17:05.121
Farrell: Move! Move! Move!

972
01:17:05.205 --> 01:17:06.790
Come on! Let's go!
Come on. move!

973
01:17:09.209 --> 01:17:11.127
[Soldiers Shouting]

974
01:17:12.712 --> 01:17:13.922
[Gunfire]

975
01:17:14.005 --> 01:17:15.340
Farrell: Enemy front!

976
01:17:15.423 --> 01:17:16.466
Bell: 2. 3—

977
01:17:16.549 --> 01:17:18.134
Farrell: 6. 7. 8. 9.

978
01:17:18.218 --> 01:17:20.053
[Bullets Whiz By]

979
01:17:21.888 --> 01:17:23.389
[Explosion]

980
01:17:28.728 --> 01:17:30.647
[Machine-Gun Fire]

981
01:17:44.911 --> 01:17:46.329
[Screams]

982
01:17:48.957 --> 01:17:51.417
Mitch. I fucking got one!

983
01:17:51.501 --> 01:17:52.794
What do you want. a fucking sweetie?

984
01:17:52.877 --> 01:17:54.170
Keep shooting. you cunt!

985
01:17:56.256 --> 01:17:58.007
[Roars]

986
01:17:58.091 --> 01:17:59.759
[Gurgles And Screams]

987
01:18:03.721 --> 01:18:04.764
[Screams]

988
01:18:07.934 --> 01:18:10.186
Fucking hell!
He bounced!

989
01:18:10.270 --> 01:18:11.688
Cease fire!

990
01:18:11.771 --> 01:18:14.107
I ain't ever seen that
in my fucking life!

991
01:18:14.190 --> 01:18:15.358
Farrell: Front 4 clear?

992
01:18:15.441 --> 01:18:16.860
Fucking hell!

993
01:18:16.943 --> 01:18:18.653
- Clear!
- Clear!

994
01:18:18.736 --> 01:18:19.946
Clear. yeah. clear.

995
01:18:20.071 --> 01:18:20.947
Soldier: Good. weren't it. eh?

996
01:18:21.030 --> 01:18:22.532
Hey. that was fucking marvelous.

997
01:18:22.615 --> 01:18:24.534
[Soldiers Chatter]

998
01:18:26.119 --> 01:18:28.204
[Chatter]

999
01:18:28.288 --> 01:18:30.039
I'm telling you. fucking marvelous.

1000
01:18:30.123 --> 01:18:32.208
Oh. hello.

1001
01:18:32.292 --> 01:18:33.793
[Soldier Wolf Whistles]

1002
01:18:36.504 --> 01:18:38.131
Listen. sweetheart...

1003
01:18:38.214 --> 01:18:41.009
you ain't gonna
be needing this anymore.

1004
01:18:41.092 --> 01:18:42.343
Eh?

1005
01:18:42.427 --> 01:18:44.220
'Cause you got me
to protect you now.

1006
01:18:44.304 --> 01:18:46.389
Soldier: Go on. Mitch.
Goon.

1007
01:18:46.472 --> 01:18:49.017
You wanna get your hands
on a really big chopper...

1008
01:18:49.100 --> 01:18:51.436
well. you just come and see me.

1009
01:18:51.519 --> 01:18:52.645
Fuck you.

1010
01:18:52.729 --> 01:18:54.063
Soldier: Well.
that's an offer. Mitch.

1011
01:18:54.147 --> 01:18:55.481
Yeah. all right.

1012
01:18:55.565 --> 01:18:56.983
How about right now?

1013
01:18:58.318 --> 01:18:59.235
Mitchell!

1014
01:19:01.779 --> 01:19:03.364
Mitchell: Easy. tiger.

1015
01:19:03.448 --> 01:19:05.241
You don't want to go
picking a fight with me. son.

1016
01:19:07.577 --> 01:19:08.494
Sergeant Farrell!

1017
01:19:08.578 --> 01:19:10.163
[Mitchell Coughs]

1018
01:19:14.000 --> 01:19:15.585
Mitchell. first action on?

1019
01:19:15.668 --> 01:19:17.045
Resecure the perimeter. sir.

1020
01:19:17.128 --> 01:19:18.254
Then get to it.

1021
01:19:18.338 --> 01:19:20.423
Jones. Bedford. go with him.

1022
01:19:22.592 --> 01:19:23.927
[Softly]
Slow down.

1023
01:19:27.931 --> 01:19:28.848
Sergeant.

1024
01:19:28.932 --> 01:19:30.391
Sir.

1025
01:19:30.475 --> 01:19:32.852
Clear the bodies off the lawn.

1026
01:19:36.481 --> 01:19:37.607
The rest of you go with him.

1027
01:19:46.449 --> 01:19:47.367
My apologies.

1028
01:19:52.163 --> 01:19:53.081
Drink?

1029
01:19:58.962 --> 01:20:01.464
Jim: Look. we're grateful. okay?

1030
01:20:01.547 --> 01:20:03.132
We're very grateful
for your protection...

1031
01:20:03.216 --> 01:20:04.467
and just having
found other people...

1032
01:20:04.550 --> 01:20:05.635
but if we're gonna
stay here—

1033
01:20:05.718 --> 01:20:06.803
Who have you killed?

1034
01:20:06.886 --> 01:20:07.804
I haven't killed anyone.

1035
01:20:07.887 --> 01:20:08.805
Since it began. who have you killed?

1036
01:20:08.888 --> 01:20:09.806
You wouldn't be alive now...

1037
01:20:09.889 --> 01:20:11.224
if you hadn't killed somebody.

1038
01:20:20.066 --> 01:20:21.067
I killed. uh—

1039
01:20:21.150 --> 01:20:22.068
I killed a boy.

1040
01:20:27.240 --> 01:20:28.157
A child?

1041
01:20:31.452 --> 01:20:32.412
Yes.

1042
01:20:34.706 --> 01:20:36.499
But you had to.

1043
01:20:36.582 --> 01:20:38.334
Otherwise. he'd have killed you.

1044
01:20:43.089 --> 01:20:44.048
Survival.

1045
01:20:48.469 --> 01:20:49.429
I understand.

1046
01:20:52.849 --> 01:20:54.017
I promised them women.

1047
01:20:57.103 --> 01:20:58.021
What?

1048
01:21:00.481 --> 01:21:02.025
8 days ago. I found Jones...

1049
01:21:02.108 --> 01:21:03.234
with his gun in his mouth.

1050
01:21:05.403 --> 01:21:06.738
He said he was going
to kill himself...

1051
01:21:06.821 --> 01:21:08.072
because there was no future.

1052
01:21:10.158 --> 01:21:11.576
What could I say to him?

1053
01:21:13.119 --> 01:21:14.495
We fight off the infected...

1054
01:21:14.579 --> 01:21:16.122
or we wait until
they starve to death...

1055
01:21:16.205 --> 01:21:17.123
and then what?

1056
01:21:19.375 --> 01:21:22.545
What do 9 men do except
wait to die themselves?

1057
01:21:22.628 --> 01:21:24.464
I moved us from the blockade...

1058
01:21:24.547 --> 01:21:26.340
I set the radio broadcasting...

1059
01:21:26.424 --> 01:21:27.508
and I promised them women...

1060
01:21:33.723 --> 01:21:35.183
'cause women mean a future.

1061
01:21:43.107 --> 01:21:45.151
Selena?

1062
01:21:45.234 --> 01:21:46.736
Hannah?

1063
01:21:46.819 --> 01:21:47.737
What is it. Jim?

1064
01:21:47.820 --> 01:21:48.738
We have to go!

1065
01:21:48.821 --> 01:21:49.739
Jim. wait—

1066
01:21:49.822 --> 01:21:51.657
No time! Come on!

1067
01:21:53.659 --> 01:21:54.827
Come on!

1068
01:21:56.871 --> 01:21:58.414
Look. we get in the cab. and we go!

1069
01:21:58.498 --> 01:21:59.415
[Whack]

1070
01:21:59.499 --> 01:22:00.541
[Selena Screams]

1071
01:22:00.625 --> 01:22:02.752
Farrell: No! You're not
gonna keep 'em here!

1072
01:22:02.835 --> 01:22:04.921
You've got to let 'em go!

1073
01:22:05.004 --> 01:22:05.922
You cannot keep 'em here!

1074
01:22:06.005 --> 01:22:06.923
Stay where you are!

1075
01:22:07.006 --> 01:22:08.257
I'll fuckin' shoot you!

1076
01:22:08.341 --> 01:22:10.510
I"m not gonna let you keep "em here!

1077
01:22:11.677 --> 01:22:13.054
You can't do this!

1078
01:22:13.137 --> 01:22:15.890
Don't any of you move!

1079
01:22:15.973 --> 01:22:17.100
Mitchell: Get hold of him!

1080
01:22:17.183 --> 01:22:18.643
Get hold of him!

1081
01:22:20.770 --> 01:22:22.772
Bedford: I can't get hold of him!

1082
01:22:22.855 --> 01:22:24.774
Mitchell: Break his fingers.
Knock him out!

1083
01:22:24.857 --> 01:22:26.943
I want to give you a chance.

1084
01:22:27.026 --> 01:22:29.529
You can be with us...

1085
01:22:30.863 --> 01:22:33.074
but I can't let them go.

1086
01:22:38.704 --> 01:22:40.456
Okay. Jim?

1087
01:22:40.540 --> 01:22:42.875
Okay.

1088
01:22:45.503 --> 01:22:47.713
Him. too.

1089
01:22:49.215 --> 01:22:51.217
[Sobbing]

1090
01:22:54.220 --> 01:22:56.222
[Gun Cocks]

1091
01:22:58.808 --> 01:23:01.519
Farrell: Marge walks onto this ship.

1092
01:23:01.602 --> 01:23:03.980
Smithers says. “Women
and seamen don't mix”...

1093
01:23:04.063 --> 01:23:05.064
and Mr. Burns says...

1094
01:23:05.148 --> 01:23:07.150
“We all know
what you think. Smithers.”

1095
01:23:07.233 --> 01:23:09.485
And that was my favorite
ever joke in The Simpsons.

1096
01:23:09.569 --> 01:23:11.279
You see.
that's what they're doing...

1097
01:23:11.362 --> 01:23:13.489
a few hundred miles from
here across the channel...

1098
01:23:13.573 --> 01:23:14.782
a-across the Atlantic.

1099
01:23:14.866 --> 01:23:16.325
They're eatin' dinner...

1100
01:23:16.409 --> 01:23:17.952
and they're watchin'
The fuckin' Simpsons.

1101
01:23:18.035 --> 01:23:21.455
They're sleeping in their
beds next to their wives...

1102
01:23:21.539 --> 01:23:22.665
